  "body": "Originally reproted [here](https://www.figma.com/file/Tf5nfkYvpbnNCo4rKLK7lS/Feedback-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=3550-240272&mode=design&t=KKDj7RS3n7oiDGfR-0)  by Francesca cc @smohamedjavid \r\n\r\nThis happens when sender sends couple of messages one by one and context menu is opened by longtap on any of those messages except first one.\r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. User A - send 2+ messages one by one\r\n2. Longtap on any message except first one\r\n3. See if Author info is shown in message preview\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** Author details are not shown\r\n\r\n![photo_2023-07-20 16 40 21](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97245802/8c570b35-5caf-43bb-9206-e12d4f01f17e)\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/97245802/891dcd4a-9f74-40aa-b191-c6d1e32a3fd9\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected result:** Author details (profile icon, name) are shown\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
